# Installation

## Git clone into `~/.dotfiles`

## Get the submodules (tmux, bashrc, etc.)

1. `git submodule init {PACKAGE}`
2. `git submodule update --merge`

## Use `GNU Stow` to create the necessary symlinks.

```bash
cd  ~/.dotfiles
stow stow    # do this first!
stow bashrc
stow vim-config
```


